       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. ACCTREAD.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       COPY CUSTOMER.
       01  END-OF-FILE PIC X VALUE 'N'.
           88 NO-MORE-ACCOUNTS VALUE 'Y'.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       0000-MAIN.
           PERFORM 1000-OPEN-FILES.
           PERFORM 2000-READ-ACCOUNT UNTIL NO-MORE-ACCOUNTS.
           CALL 'FEEPOST'.
           PERFORM 9000-CLOSE-FILES.
           STOP RUN.
       1000-OPEN-FILES.
           DISPLAY 'OPEN DAILY ACCOUNT INPUT'.
       2000-READ-ACCOUNT.
           DISPLAY 'READ CUSTOMER ' CUSTOMER-ID.
           MOVE 'Y' TO END-OF-FILE.
       9000-CLOSE-FILES.
           DISPLAY 'CLOSE DAILY ACCOUNT INPUT'.

